                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>All the miracles are numbered. The numbers 50, 81 and 87 were not used, the numbers 65, 80 and 88 were used twice.</note>
                     <note>The 1st miracle is followed by the hymn: Sobä ṣäḥafä Däqsǝyos täʾamriha ʿǝludä ... "When Däqsǝyos wrote the collection of her miracles ..." (<locus target="8rb">8rb</locus>, ls. 7-11).</note>
                     <note>Text II-5 comprises 32 strophes which are strophes 1-32 according to GrohHymn pp. 336-53.</note>
                  </msItem>
